page.title: 11Nature around School(cont.)
page.content: {2. Birds.} a) Birds seen all the year round. Sparrows, Black birds, Rooks, Kestrel, Pigeons, Starlings, Blue tits, Great tits, Song Thrush, Mistle Thrush, Moorhens, Coots, Geese, Ducks, Little owl. b)Birds seen in Summer. Finches, Yellow hammers, Wild Swans, Swallow, c)Birds seen in Winter. Robins, Lapwings, Field Fares, Red wings, {3.Animals.} Our Pond contains smooth newt,Frogs, Tadpoles,Water Snails,Fresh Water Shrimps, and some Water Spiders.In the Hedge we have seen about five Mice. At night we occasionally have visits from Rabbits and Foxes.
